agent_result:
Indeed does have a Company Reviews section, but automated access is blocked by Cloudflare verification, preventing extraction of the overall rating, total number of reviews, and review snippets. The results file (results.md) contains placeholders indicating that the data could not be retrieved.

You can manually visit a company’s review page on Indeed (e.g., https://www.indeed.com/cmp/Google/reviews) and, after passing any verification, view the rating, review count, and individual reviews.

